cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.TL, cs.SE, cs.FL 

This paper is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category as it deals with type systems and their expressive power. It could also belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-category as it involves inference and deduction. The sub-category of Theory of Computation (cs.TL) is also a possibility as it deals with the theoretical foundations of computing. The Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category is another possibility as it deals with the design and implementation of software systems. Finally, the Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL) sub-category is a possibility as it deals with the study of formal languages and their properties.
